  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_47d65bed3dc0089fde92a402f55d8f97">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Includes correspondence, laboratory and course notebooks, talks, publications, and photographs relating to Hartman's teaching career and the histories he wrote on the Materials Science Center, the Physics Department, and Applied and Engineering Physics at Cornell University. Also, unpublished lecture notes on quantum mechanics by Josef M. Jauch and A. Nordsieck.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_006c4359aac80e7c297b5400f361fdc4">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Includes a letter from Richard Feynman discussing interplanetary travel, December 5, 1945.</p>  </scopecontent>
